Ratings Pod is in CrashLoopBackoff state because MySQL Deployment was out of memory.

Resolved by restarting and or scaling up the MySQL Pod - qotd-db: 

oc delete pod -n qotd $(oc get po -n qotd|grep qotd-db|awk '{print$1}')
oc scale -n qotd --replicas=1 deployment qotd-db 
oc delete pod -n qotd $(oc get po -n qotd|grep ratings|awk '{print$1}')
